    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Areas defined by a line or narrow tract of land that separates the waters flowing into different rivers, river basins, or seas. For the areas drained by a river system, use "drainage basins."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
